quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  11,6,"Buri kiremwa cyose kigenda ku isi, Allah yakigeneye amafunguro. Kandi azi ubuturo bwacyo (ku isi) n’aho gishyikira (nyuma yo gupfa). Byose biri mu gitabo gisobanutse"
  11,7,"Ni na we waremye ibirere n'isi mu minsi itandatu, kandi intebe ye y’icyubahiro (Ar’shi) yari hejuru y’amazi; (ibyo byose yabikoze) kugira ngo abagerageze (bityo agaragaze) muri mwe urusha abandi ibikorwa byiza. Ariko uramutse ubabwiye uti \"Mu by’ukuri, muzazurwa nyuma yo gupfa\", babandi bahakanye bavuga bati \"Iyi (Qur’an) nta kindi iri cyo uretse ko ari uburozi bugaragara"
  11,8,"Kandi turamutse dukerereje ibihano kuri bo kugeza igihe cyagenwe, rwose bavuga (bannyega) bati \"Ni iki kibibujije?\" Bamenye ko umunsi (ibihano) bizabagerahonta kizabibakiza, kandi bazagotwa (n’ibihano) by’ibyo bajyaga bakerensa"
  11,9,"N’iyo dusogongeje umuntu ku mpuhwe ziduturutseho nyuma tukazimwambura, mu by’ukuri ariheba cyane ntanashimire (inema za Allah)"
  11,10,"Kandi n’iyo tumusogongeje ku byiza nyuma yo kugerwaho n'amakuba, rwose aravuga ati \"Ibibi bimvuyeho\", nuko akishima akanirata cyane"
  11,11,Uretse babandi bihanganye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza; abo bazahabwa imbabazi ndetse n'igihembo gihebuje (Ijuru)
  11,12,"Hari ubwo wowe (Muhamadi) wareka (kubagezaho) bimwe mu byo uhishurirwa, ndetse n’igituza cyawe kikaremererwa kuko bavuga bati \"Kuki atamanuriwe ubutunzi cyangwa ngo azane n’umumalayika (ushimangira ubutumwa bwe)?\"(Bagezeho ibyo uhishurirwa, kuko) mu by’ukuri, wowe uri umuburizi. Kandi Allah ni Umuhagararizi wa byose"
  11,13,"Cyangwa baravuga bati \"(Intumwa Muhamadi) yarayihimbiye (Qur’an)\". Vuga uti \"Ngaho nimuzane isura (ibice bya Qur’an) icumi mwihimbiye zimeze nka yo, maze muniyambaze abo mushoboye bose batari Allah, niba koko muri abanyakuri"
  11,14,"Ubwo nibatazibazanira, mumenye ko (Qur’an) yahishuwe biri mu bumenyi bwa Allah, kandi ko nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri itari we. Ese mwe muri abicisha bugufi (Abayisilamu)"
  11,15,"Abashaka ubuzima bwo ku isi n'imitako yayo, tuzabahembera ibikorwa byabo byuzuye bakiyiriho, ndetse nta n’ikigabanyijweho"
  11,16,"Abo ni babandi batazagira ikindi bahembwa ku munsi w’imperuka uretse umuriro, kandi ibyo bayikozeho (isi) ntacyo byabamariye, ndetse n’ibyo bakoraga byabaye impfabusa"
  11,17,"Ese uwemera ashingiye ku kuri guturutse kwa Nyagasani we (ari we Intumwa Muhamadi), maze uko kuri (Qur’an) kugakurikirwa n'umuhamya (Malayika Jibril) umuturutseho (Allah), ndetse na mbere y’uko kuri, hari igitabo cya Musa (Tawurati) cyari ubuyobozi n'impuhwe; (uwo yaba nk’ukurikira ibitagira gihamya)? Babandi bemeye (bashingiye ku kuri) ni bo bamwemera (Intumwa Muhamadi), naho abamuhakana bo mudutsiko (tw’abahakanyi), isezerano ryabo ni ukuzaba mu muriro. Bityo, ibyo ntukabishidikanyeho kuko mu by’ukuri, (iyo Qur’an) ari ukuri guturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe, ariko abenshi mu bantu ntibemera"
  11,18,"Ni nde nkozi y’ibibikurusha uhimbira Allah ikinyoma? Abo bazagezwa imbere ya Nyagasani wabo (ku munsi w’imperuka), maze abahamya (abamalayika n’abahanuzi) bavuge bati \"Aba ni bo babeshyeye Nyagasani wabo!\" Nta gushidikanya ko umuvumo wa Allah uri ku nkozi z’ibibi"
  11,19,"Babandi bakumira (abantu) kugana inzira ya Allah, bakifuza ko yatana (ngo igendere ku marangamutima yabo), kandi bagahakana imperuka"
  11,20,"Abo ntaho bacikira (ibihano bya Allah) ku isi, kandinta barinzi (babibarinda) batari Allah, ndetse bazanatuburirwa ibihano (kubera ko) batashoboraga kumva ndetse ntibanashobore kubona (ukuri)"
  11,21,"Abo ni bo bihombeje ubwabo, kandi ibyo bihimbiye (biringira ko bizabakorera ubuvugizi kwa Allah ku munsi w’imperuka) bizabatenguha"
  11,22,"Mu by’ukuri, ntagushidikanya ko ari bo bazaba abanyagihombo gihambaye ku munsi w’imperuka"
  11,23,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, ndetse bakanicisha bugufi kuri Nyagasani wabo; bazaba mu Ijuru ubuziraherezo"